  Callback
    What's the callback?
      Passing a function as a parameter another
    Use & its purpose of the callback
      executing a set of instructions after some operations ( between i/p & o/p )

      Modularizing codes in large applications, asynchrnouse programming


    Pain of callback:
      Chain of callback will result in unmanagable codebase
      Passing output from async callback function is tedious in nature
      
